28.12.2022 marked as P7. The reference for arbitration was published in the gazette. As
per page 5A of the document marked P23, the arbitration reference had been reproduced
in Gazette No. 2314/04 dated 09.01.2023. This Court finds that this was not disputed

not the Gazette that contains the referral for arbitration.
